{"tid":1563952,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！冇人知聽日有悼念義士活動？！？！","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T10:30:38.000Z","uid":186294,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5c28186c2779bcf8899a9c8b802f701b64df58","tid":1563952,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"Fb有呢個event好多日，但冇人推？有千五人喺fb填左出席，差你一個喳！<br />\n今年中秋，我地少左好多手足團圓，已離世既、被起訴既、受過傷既，多不勝數。<br />\n聽晚中秋節一齊返連儂牆，悼念已離去既手足，齊上齊落，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n[b]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n每位手足，缺一不可。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽晚7-11，連儂牆見，互相攬攬<br />\n帶個月餅，摺朵紙花，元寶蠟燭，帶給烈士</span></span><br />\n<br />\n純宗教活動，毋須不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqYK3CA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnqYK3CA.jpg&h=a0cdf1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/erhTcwP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FerhTcwP.jpg&h=9a65caaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n補fb event link：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2181497555484760/?ti=icl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2181497555484760%2F%3Fti%3Dicl&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=13e67da0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2181497555484760/?ti=icl</a><br />\n<br />\n如果擔心喺fb禁左attend會透露個人資料，可以唔禁attend，只要你地個人出席就得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n915 銅鑼灣</span>"},{"pid":"7252b953846816fa9b1fd03459ce0a055284f1fb","tid":1563952,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d74d892b403b229e711edb9549cf3818226abc83","tid":1563952,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"99e10eda204f51abcaa927acdd5f774d669f02d5","tid":1563952,"uid":186294,"like